Package mb.pso.issuesystem.entity

Class Issue.Builder

java.lang.Object
mb.pso.issuesystem.entity.Issue.Builder
Enclosing class:
Issue
public static class Issue.Builder extends Object
Builder class for creating instances of Issue. Example usage: Issue issue = new Issue.Builder() .setIssueDescription("My car is broken!") .setStatus(IssueStatus.NEW) .build();
